Spacious, comfortable and modern, Misako's Ritte hobo bag is a versatile staple that easily adapts to all your plans, whether it's a busy day at the office or a more relaxed outing around town.


Made from soft-touch faux leather, it combines a simple design with a polished finish that makes it easy to integrate into different looks. The interior offers space for everything you need in your daily routine: mobile phone, keys, purse, notebook, water bottle or even a tablet. Its metal zips and practical pockets make it easy to organise, while the magnetic button closure keeps your essentials safe at all times. Thanks to its adjustable short handle, it adapts comfortably to both everyday use and weekend getaways.


Ritte strikes a balance between aesthetics and functionality, becoming a wardrobe staple that transcends seasons. And if you're looking for something extra, combine it with the Nilus toiletries bag: together they add a play of textures and a distinctive touch that enhances your accessory set.


Features:

• Size: 33x30x14 cm

• Tone-on-tone Misako logo on the front

• Interior pocket with zip closure for small items

• Durable polyester interior lining
